Privacy Policy
What information do we collect?
* We do not collect any personal information.
* We do collect details about service stations (including fuel prices) which are provided by users.
- These are stored on our server and are able to be viewed by other users.
* We do not collect or upload your location.
* Your unique device ID.
- This is a unique key given to each device, it does not contain any personal information.
- We use the device ID to ban particular users who repeatedly enter incorrect or misleading information.
* App crashes.
- In the event of a crash, logs may be sent to help us fix and improve Fuel Map. These logs do not contain any personal deteails.
* Our website does not use cookies.
Your consent
* By using Fuel Map, you consent to our privacy policy.
Changes to our privacy policy
* If we decide to change our policy, we will post those changes on this page.
